title: Inhumans
description:
The Inhumans Chronology. This includes everything that features Black Bolt and the merry crew from Attilan, EXCEPT their original appearances in the Fantastic Four. This may appear an unforgivable omission, but even my OCD has its limits. This torrent DOES include:

1975 v1
1988 graphic novel
1990 special
1995 one shot
1998 v2 miniseries
2000 v3 (Ronan)
2003 v4
2005 Son of M*
2006 Silent War
2007 Illuminati
2008 Secret Invasion
2009 Mighty Avengers
2009 War of Kings
2010 Realm of Kings
2010 The Thanos Imperative
2013 New Avengers (Illuminati)
Inhumans 2099

Many thanks to the original scanners!
* House of M and its offshoots deserves its own separate torrent, and will probably get one (if there isn't one out there already, that is)
